data.description: This corner property for sale in the coveted Lakeshore Neighborhood of San Mateo offers a truly exceptional opportunity for homebuyers. While the home may benefit from some cosmetic updates, its prime location offers unparalleled convenience. Imagine being just minutes away from the bustling Hillsdale Mall and Bridgepoint Shopping Center, where dining options are at your doorstep. But that's not all – with easy access to both Highway 101 and 92, commuting is a breeze, making your daily life more efficient than ever. For nature enthusiasts, the property is also conveniently close to the serene Foster City Lagoon, providing a tranquil escape for outdoor activities and scenic views. And for those who rely on public transportation, the Caltrain Station is just a stone's throw away, connecting you to the entire Bay Area. Don't miss your chance to embrace the promise of spacious living in a home that's perfectly positioned for your active, modern lifestyle. Seize this incredible opportunity in San Mateo's Lakeshore Neighborhood today!
